{"id": 420, "genre": 1001, "title": "你印象最深的动画片台词？", "description": "在这个点开动画片都不能理直气壮的年纪，能不能允许我怀念一把！", "record_count": 11651, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194338pZ0xKG1XREq27O3Y.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-17T14:39:51Z", "options": [{"id": 4055, "content": "你是笨蛋吗？明日香", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143228}, {"id": 4056, "content": "篮板下是我的天下！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137628}, {"id": 4058, "content": "请赐予我力量", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144237}, {"id": 4059, "content": "好讨厌的感觉~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 100877}, {"id": 4060, "content": "我找我舅舅吃猫鼠去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4061, "content": "我找我舅舅吃猫鼠去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4062, "content": "大师兄！师父被妖怪抓走了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116143}, {"id": 4011, "content": "纳尼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143896}, {"id": 4012, "content": "在强者的眼中没有弱者的席位", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143908}, {"id": 4013, "content": "大师兄，师傅被妖怪抓走了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143910}, {"id": 4397, "content": "我还回回来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146193}, {"id": 4115, "content": "等价交换", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144744}, {"id": 4117, "content": "要死也要给我在重要的东西身边挥剑挥到死啊。——《银魂》", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86709}, {"id": 4118, "content": "喜羊羊，村长又被灰太狼抓走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143204}, {"id": 3903, "content": "红色神鹰～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136779}, {"id": 3905, "content": "隐藏黑暗力量的钥匙啊 ，在我面前显示你真正的力量 ,跟你定下约定的小樱命令你 ,封印解除 ！", "image": null, "praise_count": 270, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135605}, {"id": 3907, "content": "爷爷，有妖精！！！！！！！！！", "image": "img/option/option/20160605212004rSxVgCcdwlYFTvaU.jpeg", "praise_count": 322, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 3908, "content": "启动超级变换形态", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234940mBpjodvATxkI5PRw.jpg", "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 3910, "content": "我还会回来的", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004630NyQvzlnadF9tMTGO.jpg", "praise_count": 366, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 4283, "content": "Yes，my lord.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144765}, {"id": 3880, "content": "我不愉快～", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235005lFuKCNAoikjSBwrD.jpg", "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142454}, {"id": 3881, "content": "村长......", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143237}, {"id": 4096, "content": "希巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144565}, {"id": 4090, "content": "师傅又被妖精抓走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144542}, {"id": 4091, "content": "还差的远呢", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234952HktQY309SlPjW7xm.jpg", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144545}, {"id": 4092, "content": "你的下句话是。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144546}, {"id": 4093, "content": "沉醉在本大爷的美技中吧", "image": "img/option/option/201606042349537kiMPObtyDpl48AE.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144545}, {"id": 4094, "content": "如果我手里没有剑，就无法保护你；如果我一直握着剑，就无法抱紧你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144552}, {"id": 4095, "content": "一劈炸裂，劈浪光力枪！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144556}, {"id": 4164, "content": "大圣~~~", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234906bpY7grfUJVOZS9NP.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109916}, {"id": 4166, "content": "海绵宝宝~海绵宝宝~海绵宝~宝~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131118}, {"id": 4253, "content": "雅蠛蝶~~~\n(语气自己脑补)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38139}, {"id": 3963, "content": "影分身", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81455}, {"id": 3965, "content": "诸君，我喜爱战争", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143591}, {"id": 3967, "content": "师傅，师傅～有妖气～吃俺老孙一棒。我还没用力，你就倒下了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540826}, {"id": 3968, "content": "很遗憾\n赞数随图片序数递减。\n跟内容本身并没有什么卵关系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119861}, {"id": 3969, "content": "战斗力只有五的渣渣！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141720}, {"id": 3970, "content": "  螺旋丸！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143647}, {"id": 3971, "content": "不可以逃避，不可以逃避，不可以逃避，不可以逃避，不可以逃避", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139738}, {"id": 3972, "content": "冒个泡收藏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 3961, "content": "我来组成头部！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142244}, {"id": 4359, "content": "咦！血…………！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101526}, {"id": 4202, "content": "错的不是我们 是这个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145543}, {"id": 4217, "content": "灰太狼的：我会再回来的！....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139534}, {"id": 4070, "content": 